description.narrative:
According to the partner report it can be concluded that:
Component 1: Core Grants: 100% of plan was achieved.
Component 2: Capacity Development and Technical Assistance
Activities financed and completed under this component included, in addition to the implementation of the individual capacity development plans for each of the partners, the following:
- Development of strategic plans for the partner CSOs;
- Implementation of a biannual assessment of Shafaqs effectiveness and design of Shafaqs capacity development plan;
- Carrying out a baseline study and an independent midterm evaluation;
- Annual audits;
- Development of a Human Rights Based Approach (HRBA) manual; and training on HRBA.
Component 3: Project Management NDC successfully completed the grant administration and associated capacity building under the project and included; capacity building and technical assistance, management of the grants to the partners and oversight of the partner NGOs.
